properties.description:
Holland & Knight and Carta are excited to host Boston Tech Week’s premier Casino Night.

We’re joined by table sponsors:

- Sunset, helping startups wind down cleanly, handling legal, tax, and turning data into recovery value;
- Sightglass, a product and technology studio helping Seed to Series C founders ship faster and scale smarter;
- the Boston Club;
- Beyond 2%.

This invite-only gathering brings together founders, investors, and ecosystem leaders for a night of poker, cocktails, and high-quality networking in a casino-style setting.

Guests will enjoy professionally run games, light bites, and drinks while connecting with peers across the venture and startup ecosystem.

No real money is required to participate. Just come ready for good hands, great company, and an unforgettable night in Boston.

This event is a part of #BosTechWeek—a week of events hosted by VCs and startups to bring together the tech ecosystem. Learn more at www.tech-week.com
